{"lemma":"سَلِيلِ","slug":"سَلِيلِ","root":"س.ل.ل","root_slug":"س-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20293"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"descendant, offshoot"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"drawn, unsheathed"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Of the root س ل ل (s l l). The lexicographers say it means “male foetus”, “horse-foal”, ”any animal that is born with yet the fetal membrane on”; it is hence plausible that this word is an earlier borrowing of the same Aramaic source as assumed for شَلِيل (šalīl), see there."},"ipa":["/sa.liːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20293","headword_ar":"سَلِيلٌ","root":"sl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawn"},{"kind":"text","text":"sword;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoluwlN","text_ar":"مَسْلُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male offspring;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[because drawn forth;] (S, M, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sulaAlapN","text_ar":"سُلَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, Mgh, Msb, K;) metonymically so termed: (Mgh:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it comes forth from the belly of its mother;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓ the latter; the former so called because created from the [sperma genitalis, which is termed]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sulaAlap","text_ar":"سُلَالَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Akh, TA:) fem. of the former ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliylapN","text_ar":"سَلِيلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a daughter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A colt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) and with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a filly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, TA;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"being affixed, though"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"slyl","text_ar":"سليل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", because the word is made a subst.: (Ham p. 102:) or, as some say, (M, in the K “ and ”) the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a colt that is born not in a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"membrane such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAsikap","text_ar":"مَاسِكَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in one such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salFY","text_ar":"سَلًى"},{"kind":"text","text":": if in either of these, it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baqiyrN","text_ar":"بَقِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buqayorN","text_ar":"بُقَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the CK]. (M, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duEomuwSN","text_ar":"دُعْمُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young camel when just born, before it is known whether it is a male or a female."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pure, beverage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wine;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) as though gently drawn away from dust or motes or particles of rubbish or the like: such is said to be the beverage, or wine, of Paradise: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cool beverage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is clear from dust"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"motes"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"particles of rubbish"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, and from turbidness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is easy"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its descent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sulaAlapN","text_ar":"سُلَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salosaAlN","text_ar":"سَلْسَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"channel of the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place in which the water flows, in a valley:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle of a valley,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where flows the main body of water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wide"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and deep"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"valley,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that gives growth to the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salam","text_ar":"سَلَم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samur","text_ar":"سَمُر"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that gives growth to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salam","text_ar":"سَلَم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEap","text_ar":"ضَعَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yanamap","text_ar":"يَنَمَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Halamap","text_ar":"حَلَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAl~N","text_ar":"سَالٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (M, K:) or this latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which are trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a narrow channel of a torrent in a valley:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a low place surrounded by what is elevated, in which the water collects:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(En-Nadr, TA:) pl. of both"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sul~aAnN","text_ar":"سُلَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or of the former accord. to Kr, (M, TA,) and of the latter accord. to As [and the S], (TA,) or that of the latter is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawaAl~u","text_ar":"سَوَالُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (En-Nadr, K, TA.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliylN mino samurK","text_ar":"سَلِيلٌ مِنْ سَمُرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAl~N mino salamK","text_ar":"غَالٌّ مِنْ سَلَمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) The phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAla Als~aliylu bihimo","text_ar":"سَالَ السَّلِيلُ بِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide and deep, valley,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flowed with them"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is used by the poet Zuheyr (S, IB) as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they journeyed swiftly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IB, TA.)       -A4-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brain of the horse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hump of the camel."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuxaAE","text_ar":"نُخَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spinal cord"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliylu All~aHomi","text_ar":"سَلِيلُ اللَّحْمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portions that are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSiyl","text_ar":"خَصِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSiylapN","text_ar":"خَصِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of flesh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the former word in this case being app. a coll. gen. n., of which the n. un. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliylapN","text_ar":"سَلِيلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.); the more probably as it is added that] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salaAy^ilu","text_ar":"سَلَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Akh","TA","S","M","Msb","K","As","IB"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}